<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MP3 Property Solutions, LLC</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin:0;
background:#111;
color:white;
}

header{
background:#1b2b1b;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
}

header h1{
margin:0;
color:#7fa36b;
}

nav{
text-align:center;
background:black;
padding:10px;
}

nav a{
color:#7fa36b;
margin:0 15px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

section{
padding:40px 20px;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:60px 20px;
}

.hero h2{
color:#7fa36b;
font-size:36px;
}

.services{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.card{
background:#1a1a1a;
padding:20px;
border-left:4px solid #7fa36b;
}

.contact{
background:#1b2b1b;
padding:30px;
text-align:center;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
background:black;
font-size:14px;
}

button{
background:#7fa36b;
border:none;
padding:12px 20px;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>MP3 Property Solutions, LLC</h1>
<p>Home & Business Improvements in Richmond, VA</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#services">Services</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Reliable Property Improvement Services</h2>
<p>Serving Richmond, Virginia with quality home and business improvement solutions.</p>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>
MP3 Property Solutions, LLC provides professional home and business improvement services in Richmond, VA.
We focus on quality work, reliability, and customer satisfaction. Whether you need repairs,
upgrades, or general improvements, we are ready to help bring your property to the next level.
</p>
</section>

<section id="services">
<h2>Our Services</h2>

<div class="services">

<div class="card">
<h3>Home Improvements</h3>
<p>Repairs, upgrades, and improvements for residential properties.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Business Improvements</h3>
<p>Professional improvement solutions for offices and commercial spaces.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Property Maintenance</h3>
<p>Reliable maintenance services to keep your property in top shape.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>General Repairs</h3>
<p>Fast and dependable repair services when you need them most.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p><strong>Phone:</strong> (559) 765-8351</p>

<p><strong>Email:</strong> Mp3propertysolutions@gmail.com</p>

<p><strong>Location:</strong> Richmond, VA</p>

<br>

<a href="tel:15597658351">
<button>Call Now</button>
</a>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 MP3 Property Solutions, LLC
</footer>

</body>
</html>
